01:49:08,310 --> 01:49:12,681
My country also insists
on Francis Gary Powers.

1813
01:49:12,715 --> 01:49:13,782
No!

1814
01:49:16,318 --> 01:49:17,653
(SPEAKING GERMAN)

1815
01:49:18,854 --> 01:49:22,525
This is how things
became so confused.

1816
01:49:22,558 --> 01:49:25,294
Powers. What use
