1847
01:51:14,570 --> 01:51:16,572
Yes, I hesitate to say
it's excellent.

1848
01:51:16,605 --> 01:51:17,473
But it's excellent,
sir.

1849
01:51:17,506 --> 01:51:19,541
Good, good.
Good.

