1907
01:53:47,623 --> 01:53:48,991
You fucked it all up!

1908
01:53:49,024 --> 01:53:50,826
Oh, don't worry.

1909
01:53:50,859 --> 01:53:52,961
I think it's
gonna be fine.

1910
